        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PRC Military and Human Rights Capital Markets Sanctions Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits&amp;nbsp;U.S. persons from investing in securities issued by certain sanctioned and otherwise restricted entities, including Chinese military companies and Chinese entities sanctioned for human rights abuses or corruption.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill establishes divestment deadlines and criminal and civil penalties for violations of the bill.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
